NAME
       pbmclean - flip isolated pixels in portable bitmap

SYNOPSIS
       pbmclean [-connect] [pbmfile]

DESCRIPTION
       Reads  a  portable  bitmap  as  input.  Outputs a portable
       bitmap with  every  pixel  which  has  less  than  connect
       (default  1)  identical neighbours inverted.  Pbmclean can
       be used to clean up "snow" on bitmap images.

